oai_dc:dc.dc:description: SUFFRAGE CELEBRATION ON MRS. CATT'S RETURN NEW YORK, Aug. 20.—The National American Woman Suffrage association announced Thursday night plans for a celebration on the return of its presi- dent, Mrs. Carrie Chapman Catt, from Nashville, after winning ratification of the nineteenth amendment by the thirty-sixth state.
